  "keyFeatures": [
    "Zero-config scaffolding with interactive prompts",
    "Support for Express and Fastify frameworks",
    "Multiple database options (MySQL, PostgreSQL, MongoDB)",
    "ORM integration (Prisma, Drizzle, Mongoose)",
    "Built-in JWT authentication support",
    "Docker and GitHub Actions setup",
    "TypeScript-first approach with ESM support",
    "Production-ready project structure"
